WEBVTT

00:03:59.960 --> 00:04:03.519
or that there is an Indian
women’s cricket team.

00:04:03.520 --> 00:04:04.640
In those days,

00:04:04.641 --> 00:04:07.359
there was nothing 
in women’s cricket, not even money.

00:04:07.360 --> 00:04:11.199
We had to sponsor ourselves for tours.

00:04:11.200 --> 00:04:17.370
Back then, Dad decided to turn me
into a professional cricketer,

00:04:17.370 --> 00:04:19.639
which was a big decision for him.

00:04:19.640 --> 00:04:23.639
This journey would have been very 
difficult without his support.

00:04:23.640 --> 00:04:27.599
I am from a south Indian Tamilian family,

00:04:27.600 --> 00:04:30.290
so all my cousins are into academics